# Aurora slope-stretch repro (host side). Spawn the host mech at the
# base of Aurora's west hill (~x=20 tiles = 640 px world; floor is at
# ~y=H-4 = ~2752 px). Walk right (uphill) for several seconds. The
# stretch bug should manifest visibly in the screenshots.
#
# Aurora is 160 tiles wide × 90 tall; t2w(x) = x*32. floor_y = (90-4)*32 = 2752.
# West hill rises from t2w(20)=640 to peak at t2w(32)=1024 with
# hill_peak_y = t2w(H-11) = t2w(79) = 2528.

window 1280 720
out build/shots/net/2p_slope_aurora.host
network host 24073
name HostA
map aurora
spawn_at 600 2700

mouse 1100 360

at 60   shot lobby_full
at 200  shot match_t200_pre
at 240  press right
at 260  shot match_t260_climb1
at 290  shot match_t290_climb2
at 320  shot match_t320_climb3
at 360  shot match_t360_climb4
at 400  release right
at 420  shot match_t420_stopped
at 540  shot summary
at 600  end
